<bibRefCitation author="Anker, A. &amp; De Grave, S." box="[302,454,1674,1699]" pageId="12" pageNumber="491" pagination="343 - 454" refId="ref11825" refString="Anker, A. &amp; De Grave, S. (2016) An updated and annotated checklist of marine and brackish caridean shrimps of Singapore (Crustacea, Decapoda). Raffles Bulletin of Zoology, 34, 343 - 454." type="journal article" year="2016">Grave (2016</bibRefCitation>
